OS_BinaryToDecimal  (&28)
#Parent OS_
=>	R0 =	integer
	R1 =	pointer to buffer
	R2 =	size of buffer
<=	R2 =	length of string

This SWI converts a 32 bit integer to a string. Why we have this call, is a bit unclear, as <OS_ConvertInteger4=>OS_Convert> should do the same.
